Philips Inspiration Elite Nebulizer (Brown and Grey) Price: Rs.2500

Key Features

  • Sidestream Disposable Nebulizer
  • 0.55 Amps Current
  • 150° C Thermal Overload Protector
The Philips Inspiration Elite Respironics Nebulizer could be an ideal medical equipment for those of you diagnosed with respiratory ailments as it capably provides a quick and reliable delivery of medication. This Compressor Inspiration Nebulizer utilizes compressed air to transform your liquid medication into fine aerosol or vapor-like particles that can be effectively inhaled by you through a mouthpiece or a face mask.

This medication in aerosol form is delivered directly to your lungs leading to an efficient and quicker treatment time. Crafted to cater to both adults and children anyone irrespective of their age can use this Inspiration Elite Respironics Nebulizer.

Body

The Inspiration Elite Respironics Nebulizer by Philips is designed for easy operation and convenient usage as the device is compact and robust. Weighing about 1500 g this nebulizer is lightweight and portable enabling you to carry it with you even if you are travelling. This Respironics Nebulizer comes in four main components comprising of the compressor unit air tube medication cup and a mouthpiece with the option of using a face mask as well.

Built to provide enhanced convenience the main unit is designed with handset docking. You can place your medication cup and mouthpiece on the dock allowing easy handling of the equipment. The main unit houses an easy-to-use on/off switch and a connector that links the main unit to the mouthpiece and medication cup by air tubing. The medication cup holds sufficient amount of medication which is just right for your treatment. You also have the option of using a face mask or mouthpiece to inhale the prescribed medication. The face masks come in different sizes suitable for both adults and children.

Performance

The Philips Inspiration Elite Respironics Nebulizer operates at an average air flow rate of 5.4 slpm therefore capable of delivering a high concentration of aerosol to the narrow branches in the lower airways of your lungs. Equipped with a Thermal Overload Protector that has a variable trip temperature of up to 150 degree Celsius the machine automatically switches off the current supply to the compressor preventing excessive flow of current.

This Philips Nebulizer also comes with filters that reduce the chance of infection by removing bacteria from the gas delivered to your lungs thereby meeting hygiene and health standards. The nebulizer provides you with four spare filters as it is always advisable to change your filters regularly to ensure that the air you breathe in is clean. The Respironics compressor Nebulizer consumes 50 W of electricity and requires a power supply of 230 V 50 Hz for a sound functioning.
